{
  "id": "adv_bond_kan_01_03",
  "title": "kana3",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん、ふーん……ここのセレクトショップの服\nどれもオシャレなんだよね。今日は何買おうかな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmー‚ hmmー… the clothes at this select shop\nAnything is stylish. What should I buy today~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5229249955
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "ん……あれは、こころ？\nなんかめっちゃこそこそしてるけど、もしかして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Umm… is that Kokoro?\nShe's acting all sneaky‚ maybe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5229249955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.9516100884
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "ははーん、よし、面白そうだから声掛けてみようっと\nねえ、あんた、そんな所で何してんのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaー‚ good‚ it looks fun‚ so I'll try to talk\nHey‚ you‚ what are you doing in a place like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.9516100884,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5915.0565783
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.7784123739
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "ぎくっ！　か、kanaさん！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Prick! k‚ kana-san!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.7784123739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.0257593474
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "な、何って……お洋服屋さんなんですから\n服を買いに来たに決まってるじゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-What are you doing… it's a clothing store‚\nisn’t it natural to come here to buy clothes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0257593474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.3248522124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "その割にはなんかこそこそしてない？　 もしかして\nこんな大人なお店に私がいても大丈夫かな……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something like that‚ didn't you feel a little sneaky? Maybe\nwould it be okay for me to be in such a grown-up store…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3248522124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "場違いじゃないかな……でもこういう服着てみたいな\nとか、そんな風に悩んじゃってた感じ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if I got the wrong place… but I want to wear something like this\nIt seems like you were thinking about this~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2875506085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.2003628733
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、こんな姿人に見られたら恥ずかしいよね？　ごめん\n気付かないフリしとけば良かったかな？　きゃはっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ it'd be embarrassing if someone saw you like this? Sorry\nMaybe I should have pretended not to notice? Haha!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2003628733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.1651926679
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなことは……！　普段からこころも\nこういう大人の店で優雅に試着して服を買うんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-That's not…! Kokoro normally\ntry on clothes elegantly and purchase them at grown-up shops like this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1651926679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.9468028388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "バレバレの嘘ついちゃって可愛い～！　てか、十代の\nお子ちゃまは隣のショッピングモールで十分だろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's so cute tell flagrant lies~! But‚ for a teenager‚\nthe shopping mall next door is enough",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9468028388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.4281407994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "くっ……こころのことバカにしてますね……\nそ、そういうkanaさんこそ、どうなんでしょうね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… she's treating Kokoro like an idiot…\nW-What do you think about kana-san‚ who says that~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.4281407994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.4755553884
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "は？　どういう意味？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.4755553884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "見た目は大人、喋ると『精神年齢十三歳！』みたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looks like an adult‚ but when she talks \"mental age of 13!\"‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.1074147147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.1074147147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんがいくら大人っぽい服で着飾ってもねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter how adult-like the clothes kana-san wears",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.8884117367
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "結局、豚に真珠というか……。もう十代じゃないんです\nからもう少し落ち着きを持った方がいいですよ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the end‚ it's like cast pearls before swine… you're not a teenager anymore‚\nit's probably better to feel a little more calm~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.8884117367,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.4445790849
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、こころちゃん、豚って言った方が豚なんだよ～？\n知ってた～？　だからこころちゃんが豚ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Kokoro-chan‚ the one who says pig is a pig‚ right~?\nDid you know that? That's why Kokoro-chan is a pig",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4445790849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.5343748333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "何ですか、その幼稚な反撃は？\n豚さん、可愛いじゃないですか。ぶーぶー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is that‚ childish hit back?\nPigs are cute‚ aren't they? Oinkー Oinkー",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.5343748333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.0889556489
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "このクソガキ、黙ってれば好き勝手言いやがって……\n上等じゃない、こうなりゃ白黒ハッキリさせてやる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This little bastard‚ says whatever she wants when I keep quiet…\nNot fine‚ I'm going to make this clear to you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.0889556489,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.3397491695
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "今からこのお店にある服を使って\nどっちが大人なコーデを出来るか勝負よ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ using the clothes in this store‚\nwe're going to have a competition to see who can put together a more grown-up outfit!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.3397491695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.9252363127
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "おー！　楽しそうな宣戦布告！　望むところです！\nこころのファッションセンスを舐めないで下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ohー! A fun war declaration! I want it‚ too!\nDon't underestimate Kokoro's fashion sense",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.9252363127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、店員さーん。試着を……\nえ……う、うるさい？　ででで出ていけ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me‚ clerk. I'm trying on…\nEh… i-it's noisy? G-G-G-Get outta here…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.6683197261,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.7153947116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうすんのよ！　あんたのせいであの店",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you going to do! It's your fault",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.715396746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_03-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "出禁になっちゃったじゃん！　お気に入りだったのに！",
      "translations": {
